.SH NAME
.PP
mshell \- a command line interpreter written in c
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
mshell [\f[I]filename]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
mshell is a custom shell interpreter that ships with a bunch
of great featu
.PD 0
.P
.PD
